projects.name: LobangCube
projects.description: AI Hackathon Project - Won Overall Champion and Most Impactful Solution. Input your lifestyle information, then it will output 3 metrics and an overall score based on them. The metrics were produced by a Random Forest Regressor Model, and GridSearchCV was used for hyperparameter tuning.
projects.techStack: Altair, Git, pandas, NumPy, Scikit-Learn, Streamlit, SQLite

projects.name: MTG Price Aggregator
projects.description: Developed a full-stack web application using BS4 to scrape data, FastAPI as the backend, React and Material UI as the frontend. Sends a request to all the requested stores concurrently, and sends it back to the client to view all the prices.
projects.techStack: BS4, Docker, FastAPI, Git, Material UI, React

projects.name: Homelab
projects.description: It hosts media, static websites, web applications, and a VPN server. All applications and services are in their own Docker container with a compose file.
